Subject: Re: [ACPI] Re: [PATCH] PNPACPI: fix types when decoding ACPI resources [resend]
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
